{"tid":1252301,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"621已過 希望各位唔好放過借今次事件出衫食人血饅頭既含家產","createTime":"2019-06-23T02:47:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-23T03:26:35.000Z","uid":34495,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"60375303cf6989d47dbfd7b665981828b9b6249e","tid":1252301,"uid":34495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T02:47:11.000Z","msg":"自從612之後就好多IG Shop出Po整Tee想襯機賺一筆，仲自稱會用成本價Sell啲垃圾Tee，但佢啲成本價就成70蚊，例如呢間：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2z3i0Mp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2z3i0Mp.jpg&h=3cfd95d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rK6pyPF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrK6pyPF.jpg&h=96310861&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RxnvRSX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRxnvRSX.jpg&h=d425f012&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/oteehk?igshid=12f52n7hxnjkx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Foteehk%3Figshid%3D12f52n7hxnjkx&d=UYGl2U%2FUD6QdVJGaYMmpaF8MSy0xNzs2bKpftArA8vk%3D&h=e3a0bb11\" target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/oteehk?igshid=12f52n7hxnjkx</a><br />\n<br />\n而根據熟悉做衫既巴打所講，呢啲Tee<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">成本價都係20-30不等</span></strong>，咁請問你咩撚野廠咁巴閉成70蚊一件成本？<br />\n<br />\n而且經過向原作者查詢有無授權俾佢作商業用途後得到以下答覆：<br />\n<br />\n<strong>謝謝您的告知~~ <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">目前我們還未授權商業性的服飾印製喔!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n馬賽團隊非常願意讓每位支持香港的朋友自印自用, 還請大家幫忙支持香港 也尊重著作權~&nbsp;<br />\n再次感謝你告知!!🙁</strong><br />\n<br />\n當巴打上去質問佢有無得到人地授權既時候佢係Block哂咁多位連登仔，即係佢都心知肚明係無得到授權係偷人Design賺錢，實在其心可誅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">各位快啲入去Report間shop 食人血饅頭食得你咁過癮</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p